column2: SELECT ALL   m.OBJID AS OBJID,   m.RA AS RA,   m.DEC AS DEC,      n.objid AS WISE_ID,      w.w1mag,   n.distance AS SEPARATION_AKARI_WISE /*   INTO   mydb.AKARIx3#AllWise */   FROM    MyDB.akari AS a,   WISE_allsky AS w      OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( a.RA, a.DEC, #) AS n    LEFT JOIN WISE_allsky AS o ON n.objid = w.objid    where a.OBJID < #
